{{Infobox artwork|image=Luca_Signorelli_-_Madonna_of_Mercy_and_Saints_Sebastian_and_Bernardino_da_Siena_-_Google_Art_Project.jpg|title=Our Lady of Mercy <br/>with Saints and Angels|artist=Luca Signorelli|height_metric=210|width_metric=215|museum=Diocesan Museum|city=Pienza}}
'''''Our Lady of Mercy with Saints and Angels''''' is a c.1490 painting by [[Luca Signorelli]], showing [[Our Lady of Mercy]] flanked by [[Saint Sebastian]] and [[Bernardino of Siena]]. It is now in the Diocesan Museum in [[Pienza]].

